{"tid":2442372,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"情侶分手｜女子聲稱入屋執拾物件 生果刀割前男友頸 再自插腹部重傷昏迷","createTime":"2021-03-11T10:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T13:01:32.000Z","uid":44209,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"30c8c4c27679ac847cb588a3bc95a3e5986421ef","tid":2442372,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:12:23.000Z","msg":"好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210311/QLGMKDPCZZHJNAZ5ULTPVE2RR4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210311%2FQLGMKDPCZZHJNAZ5ULTPVE2RR4%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=a776a740\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210311%2FQLGMKDPCZZHJNAZ5ULTPVE2RR4%2F&h=3132fabe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210311/QLGMKDPCZZHJNAZ5ULTPVE2RR4/</a><br />\n<br />\n早上11時50分，警方接報觀塘協和街175號合和大廈，有一名女子在一個低層單位內腹部受傷，救援人員到場發現女子已陷入昏迷，同時亦發現一名男子頸部受傷，立即將兩人送院治理。警方將案列傷人案件處理，正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，兩名傷者為一對已分手的情侶，女事主今早去到前男友的寓所，聲稱執拾自己的物件，男方則正在打機，此時女方突取出一柄生果刀，割傷男方頸部，之後女事主再將生果刀插進自己腹部，重傷昏迷，男事主負傷報警求助。"},{"pid":"ebd9f5ab045e5670585c3182757ab67f20a6a1ba","tid":2442372,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:13:18.000Z","msg":"覺得係條仔偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81518a81c46b56aa58bc1b4ea33bd28410b80021","tid":2442372,"uid":48434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:13:19.000Z","msg":"何必呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359127d38144c2bf2aaacd2cd075ecb058429e5d","tid":2442372,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:14:33.000Z","msg":"病嬌<img src=\"/