傷者陷入昏迷，面部染血，替其包紮止血後，再急送伊利沙伯醫院救治，情況危殆。男傷者頸部淌血，一併送院治療，警方封鎖現調查血案原因。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，兩傷者同姓區，原本在上址共築愛巢同居，但雙方於農曆新年期間分手。事發時男方正在打機，有人突然施襲鎅頸，男方奪過生果刀掉地後，女方再檢起刀自插腹部。"},{"pid":"a295906bcc408f57879c4f47607ba6b67adf0c27","tid":2442372,"uid":307473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:38:52.000Z","msg":"睇錯合和中心"},{"pid":"6913f6f67d1c96e76374908113e3523a19168999","tid":2442372,"uid":283908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"529b8dbf36661d01b30abecb8937c677b443956b","tid":2442372,"uid":48434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0291ef4e02cda7fa1def1fd1bc6b2bd845cd0663","tid":2442372,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81518a81c46b56aa58bc1b4ea33bd28410b80021","tid":2442372,"uid":48434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:13:19.000Z","msg":"何必呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:14:36.000Z","msg":"可能hurt得好深<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都唔得洗殺人呱🥴"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:18:55.000Z","msg":"點解要隊埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:41:28.000Z","msg":"打和"},{"pid":"f6734c77ece12f314bef7f516070405e2b80c4e2","tid":2442372,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd7b4f647e3ee1d6ccbd67c79f8ed879acc2349","tid":2442372,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:01:32.000Z","msg":"應該好撚嬲先會插埋自己肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}